PASSENGER INFORMATION
CHILDREN:
Half fare will be charged for each child two years of age or over,
but under 12, and the child will be entitled to occupy a seat. One infant (a
child under two years of age) will be transported free with an adult passenger,
but will not be entitled to a seat. Each additional infant, or one occupying a
seat, will be charged 50% of the adult fare.
CHARGES FOR LATE CANCELLATION ON DOMESTIC SERVICES:
a). Full
refund when the reserved space is cancelled 24 hours prior to departure of
the flight.
b). 25% charge if the cancellation is made less than 24 hours
but more than 3 hours prior to departure of flight (*).
c). 50% charge if
the cancellation is either made less than 3 hours prior to departure of the
flight or if the passengers fail to appear at the airport (*).
d). For groups of
more than 10 people, a special regulation applies. Please request details.
(*) These charges will apply only on that portion of the flight for which
reservations have been made. In order to avoid these charges, we request our
customers that if their trip is not going to be made, to please cancel reser
vations as far in advance as possible.
RECONFIRMATIONS ON INTERNATIONAL SERVICES:
Return or continuing
reservations must be reconfirmed after a stopover, not later than 24 hours
before departure time. Unless this notice of intention to. use such return or
continuing reservations is received by Mexicana or an authorized agent 24
hours or more prior to departure time, the previously confirmed reservations
will be automatically canceiled. Passengers making reconfirmations must
indicate an address or telephone number at which they may be reached in the
city where the plane is to be boarded.
BAGGAGE:
Each full or half-fare passenger, on MEXICANA, will be entitled
to 25 kilos (55 pounds) baggage allowance free of charge.
ARRIVAL TO AIRPORT:
Passengers must be at the airport at least 45 minutes
prior to the scheduled departure time for domestic flights and 60 minutes for
international flights. Carrier assumes no liability in case of passengers who
arrive later than stipulated here, and cannot be transported.
FARES AND SCHEDULES:
All fares and schedules shown herein are for infor-
mation purposes only, and are subject to change and correction without notice.
